Package org.jamwiki.validator

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    RequestValidator
    Interface used when determining whether or not to allow or disallow a request.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    HoneypotValidator
    Utility methods for working with the Project Honeypot API.
    ReCaptchaUtil
    Utility methods for working with the reCAPTCHA library.
    RequestValidatorInfo
    Utility class used to return information about a validation request.
    UserBlockValidator
    Validator used when determining if a request represents a user or IP address block using the wiki block list.
    UserBlockValidatorInfo
    Determine whether a request should be blocked based on the wiki blocklist.
